Title: 关键代码片段解析
Describe: 覆盖 S08_CODE_SNIPPETS。聚焦少量能代表架构边界和风险的代码片段，避免长篇源码转录。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S08_CODE_SNIPPETS - Runnable 是统一执行协议

[Description]
摘自 `libs/core/langchain_core/runnables/base.py:125` 附近：

```python
class Runnable(ABC, Generic[Input, Output]):
    """A unit of work that can be invoked, batched, streamed, transformed and composed.

    Key Methods
    ===========

    - `invoke`/`ainvoke`: Transforms a single input into an output.
    - `batch`/`abatch`: Efficiently transforms multiple inputs into outputs.
    - `stream`/`astream`: Streams output from a single input as it's produced.
```

[UML]
None

[Detail]
这段代码解释了为什么 core 层能承载模型、工具、chain、retriever 等不同对象：它们都可以被视为 `Runnable`，并获得 sync、async、batch、stream 和组合能力。维护上要注意，`Runnable` 的 docstring 和方法契约不是内部细节，partner、agent 和用户 chain 都依赖这个协议。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
init_chat_model 的安全边界

[Description]
摘自 `libs/langchain_v1/langchain/chat_models/base.py:311` 附近：

```python
configurable_fields: Which model parameters are configurable at runtime:

    - `None`: No configurable fields (i.e., a fixed model).
    - `'any'`: All fields are configurable. **See security note below.**
    - `list[str] | Tuple[str, ...]`: Specified fields are configurable.

    !!! warning "Security note"

        Setting `configurable_fields="any"` means fields like `api_key`,
        `base_url`, etc., can be altered at runtime, potentially redirecting
        model requests to a different service/user.
```

[UML]
None

[Detail]
这段不是普通参数说明，而是运行时信任边界。`_ConfigurableModel` 会从 `config.configurable` 提取字段并在真正调用时实例化模型；如果允许 `any`，用户或上层配置可以改 provider endpoint 和凭据。安全建议是对非可信输入显式列出 `configurable_fields`，不要把 `api_key`、`base_url`、代理配置等交给外部请求控制。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
create_agent 的 graph 编译出口

[Description]
摘自 `libs/langchain_v1/langchain/agents/factory.py:1671` 附近：

```python
return graph.compile(
    checkpointer=checkpointer,
    store=store,
    interrupt_before=interrupt_before,
    interrupt_after=interrupt_after,
    debug=debug,
    name=name,
    cache=cache,
    transformers=[
        ToolCallTransformer,
        SubagentTransformer,
        *middleware_transformers,
        *(transformers or ()),
    ],
).with_config(config)
```

[UML]
None

[Detail]
这段是 agent 工厂从“构建图”到“返回可运行对象”的出口。`checkpointer`、`store`、interrupt、debug、name、cache 和 transformers 都在这里固化为 compiled graph 行为。新增 transformer 或 middleware 变更顺序会影响 streaming 输出、tool call 展示和 subagent 行为；评审这类改动时需要同时看 tool loop、interrupt 和 stream 场景。

